name: Vendcoin
description:
$VEND is the art utility and trading token for the Vending Machine that gives you exclusive discounts on machine use and future events. As a holder of the $VEND token you support the growth of the Tezos De-Fi art ecosystem in a way that is uniquely part of the spirit of community and the arts on Tezos.

$XTZ raised during this IFO will fund initial liquidity pools and community rewards, as well as upgrades and maintenance to the Vending Machine for future iteration and use. $VEND sold during the IFO will be locked for 10 days and then farmed over the next 90 days.

Lets unlock the creative and economic spirit of the future on Tezos via the power of the Vending Machine.
